Mary Nnah For the last 8 years, philanthropist and women empowerment activist; Adesunmbo Adeoye has anchored the Inspiring Change Conference, with a host of various influential Nigerian women. This year, the prestigious brand hosts its 9th Edition, themed “Run Forward”. Kicking off the activities online, the conference will host its speakers to intense clubhouse conversations by 8 pm daily, from Tuesday, March 8th to Friday 11th. It will be very intentional towards addressing current societal issues. To conclude the lineup of events, the physical gathering will take place on Saturday, March 12th at the Wisdom Arena, Agege by 10 am. Organisers believe the year 2022 is the year of prominence, where you need the right network of influence to propel you to take the right step into your next level and annual free gathering of positive like minds, therefore this year’s Inspiring Change Conference promises loads of knowledge, tips on personal and business growth, and many more with a lineup boasts of an impressive lineup of experienced speakers. Taking the stage this year are @davidoadeoye; Life and Business Coach, @mary.akpobome; Financial Executive Director @officialiniabims; Business Executive, @tosinolaseinde; CEO, Money Africa @ifys.kitchen; Lawyer & Foodie @bibiadeniyi; Fashion Designer and @oyindamolaossi; Human Resources Professional coming on board to inspire you to “RUN FORWARD” towards your goal. It’s going to be both empowering and motivational. Registeration is done at https://bit.ly/runforward whole interested person can follow the conversation on social media: #inspiringchangeconference2022 #inspiringchangeconference #runforward2022 #icc2022 #IWD2022 #Adesunmboadeoyeinitiative Link in bio @inspiringchangeng @sunmboadeoye